Set lenght to 0
Set wordCount to 0
Set vowelCount to 0
Note vowel is (a,e,i,o,u)
Read sentence as a string
For each character in sentence
Begin
lenght += 1
If character is a space then wordCount +=1
Else if character is a vowel then vowelCount +=1
Else character is a point then exit the loop
Print lenght
Print wordCount + 1
Print vowelCount
End